# 一个是某某目录下的所有文件：目录名/，所有某某后缀的文件：*.，忽略某个文件，直接写文件名，注意路径，根目录可以直接写文件名，其他要加路径
# Python bytecode and caches
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.pyre/
.coverage
.coverage.*
coverage.xml
htmlcov/

# Virtual environments and local Python tooling
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/
.uv-cache/

# Build and packaging artifacts
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.eggs/
*.egg
.Python

# Node / frontend
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
vite-dev.log
vite-dev.err.log

# Frontend build and tool caches
.vite/
.turbo/
.next/
out/

# Environment and secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.local
config.ini
secret.json

# ZBot runtime data
logs/
memory/
cache/
temp/
tmp/
.ZBot/
~/

# Local databases and large model/data artifacts
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3
*.pth
*.pt
*.bin
*.ckpt
*.safetensors

# Archives
*.zip
*.rar
*.tar
*.tar.gz
*.tgz
*.7z

